  "content": "00; margin-bottom: 6px;\">Your iGPU is free compute.</div>\n        <div style=\"font-size: 17px; color: var(--text-secondary);\">Split workloads instead of fighting for one GPU.</div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"divider\" style=\"margin: 0;\"></div>\n    <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 24px;\">\n      <div style=\"width: 80px; height: 80px; border-radius: 50%; background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.15); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 40px; flex-shrink: 0;\">&#128268;</div>\n      <div>\n        <div style=\"font-size: 24px; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 6px;\">ONNX sessions are independent.</div>\n        <div style=\"font-size: 17px; color: var(--text-secondary);\">One on CUDA, one on OpenVINO, one on CPU. All parallel.</div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"divider\" style=\"margin: 0;\"></div>\n\n    <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 24px;\">\n      <div style=\"width: 80px; height: 80px; border-radius: 50%; background: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.15); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 40px; flex-shrink: 0;\">&#128736;</div>\n      <div>\n        <div style=\"font-size: 24px; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 6px;\">Detect at startup, not at build time.</div>\n        <div style=\"font-size: 17px; color: var(--text-secondary);\">One binary. Probe hardware. Pick backends. Fall back gracefully.</div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"divider\" style=\"margin: 40px 0;\"></div>\n\n  <div style=\"text-align: center;\">\n    <div style=\"font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text-primary); margin-bottom: 16px;\">\n      Running local inference on<br>heterogeneous hardware?\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"font-size: 20px; color: var(--text-secondary);\">\n      Curious what setups people have landed on &#128071;\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"flex-grow\"></div>\n  <div class=\"author-tag\">Lim Chun Zhe</div>\n  <div class=\"slide-number\">08 / 08</div>\n</div>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n",
